'''National Intelligence Coordinating Agency ''' or '''NICA''' is the primary intelligence collection and analysis arm of the Philippine government in charge in carrying out overt, [[covert]], and [[clandestine]] intelligence programs. The current head of the Agency is General [[Cesar Garcia]]. Its motto is ''Ang Karunungan ay Kaligtasan'' ([[translation]] Knowledge is Security).